&END

&CPMD
  USE_CUFFT 
  FFT_N_STREAMS_PER_DEVICE
  2
  FFT_N_DEVICES_PER_TASK
  1
  USE_CUBLAS
  BLAS_N_STREAMS_PER_DEVICE
  2
  BLAS_N_DEVICES_PER_TASK
  1
  QMMM
  QUENCH BO
  MOLECULAR DYNAMICS CP
  ISOLATED MOLECULE
  CENTER MOLECULE
  MAXSTEP
   2
  MAXITER
   5
